parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
passenger-side airbag deploys but does not inflate
driver-side airbag does not deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in receiving a replacement airbag inflator can leave the vehicle occupant at risk of serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Notification of recall received
but parts are unavailable
dealer unable to provide a time frame for repair
multiple calls to dealer and manufacturer with no resolution.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of control of the vehicle can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Steering wheel locks up
vehicle becomes difficult to control
driver loses control of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, slow down, and even come to a complete stop, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips
hesitates
or fails to engage
causing the vehicle to lose power
slow down
or come to a complete stop. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The throttle body failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, slow down, and even come to a complete stop, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
slows down
or comes to a complete stop without warning. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission harsh shifting can cause the vehicle to jerk, hesitate, or fail to engage, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts harshly
hesitates
or fails to engage
causing the vehicle to jerk or hesitate. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The clutch failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, slow down, and even come to a complete stop, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Evaporator Discharge Air Temperature Sensor
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the evaporator discharge air temperature sensor can cause the air conditioning system to malfunction, leading to discomfort and potential health risks due to high temperatures.
symptoms: The air conditioning system does not function properly
emitting hot or fluctuating air
and the vehicle's temperature gauge may not provide accurate readings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the smart junction box can cause the turn signals, brake lights, and other electrical systems to malfunction, leading to safety risks and accidents.
symptoms: Turn signals and brake lights do not function
and the dashboard may display warning lights or messages.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the engine to stall or hesitate, leading to loss of power and control, and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls or hesitates
and the dashboard may display warning lights or messages.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition coils can cause the engine to stall or misfire, leading to loss of power and control, and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls or misfires
and the dashboard may display warning lights or messages.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Lock and Door Handle Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the power locks and door handles can cause difficulties in entering or exiting the vehicle, and increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power locks and door handles do not function properly
and the doors may not open or close correctly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning light can indicate a malfunction of the air bag system, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The air bag warning light illuminates on the dashboard.
